(57, '24.231.188.208', 1334342057, 924, 0, 'Question #924: I\\\'m reporting question #924 because ... \r\n\r\n\\"Only\\" is NOT in 10.3.4, and that word totally changes the meaning of the sentence. That particular rule is *allowing* players to play with doctor\\\'s clearance. The only thing that would *disallow* previously-injured skaters from playing is the Head Ref\\\'s discretion. There\\\'s not an explicit rule against injured skaters playing.', 2),
