(113, '99.107.231.114', 1336775883, 713, 0, 'Question #713: I\\\'m reporting question #713 because ... \r\n\r\n\\"When to major penalties on Blockers expire?\\" would be better.', 3),
(114, '99.107.231.114', 1336776123, 772, 0, 'Question #772: I\\\'m reporting question #772 because ... \r\n\r\nOkay, I admit that this is nitpicky, but if a skater fouls out with anything more than zero minors, then those minors \\"didn\\\'t count\\" towards her fouling out. For example, should could foul out (with her 7th trip to the box having been caused by a Major penalty) with 7 majors, and 3 minors. The 3 minors didn\\\'t count.\r\n\r\nThanks again for doing this project, it\\\'s been a huge help to me.', 3),
(115, '99.107.231.114', 1336776225, 942, 0, 'Question #942: I\\\'m reporting question #942 because ... \r\n\r\nWouldn\\\'t she also lose her Lead Jammer status when a teammate removed her cover? \r\n\r\nI think yes.\r\n', 1),
(116, '94.0.178.38', 1336782712, 312, 0, 'Question #312: I\\\'m reporting question #312 because ... option d. \\"Breaking\\" is incorrectly spelled; the correct spelling should be \\"Braking\\".', 2),
