(144, '12.145.65.167', 1337369163, 676, 0, 'Question #676: I\\\'m reporting question #676 because ...\r\n\r\nThe issue of misconduct against a teammate is controversial and still a bit of grey area until there is a clarification from WFTDA.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.zebrahuddle.com/index.php?topic=2513.0', 4),
(145, '24.92.69.107', 1337621232, 946, 0, 'Question #946: I\\\'m reporting question #946 because none of the answers are correct. The relevant rule is...\r\n\r\n6.8.9 --  If a skater jumps and ceases all contact with the ground, (their) prior in bounds/out of bounds status is maintained until contact with the ground re-establishes in bounds/out of bounds status.\r\n\r\n...so maybe a \\"depends\\" answer should be added as the correct one?\r\n\r\n- Ming the Merciless\r\nMilwaukee Blitzdkrieg / Paper Valley Roller Girls / Green Bay Smackers\r\n', 3),
