(295, '184.100.39.9', 1344470222, 842, 0, 'Question #842: I\\\'m reporting question #842 because ... \r\n\r\nWhen I read WFTDA rules 9.1.1 it states \\"It is strongly encouraged that at least one referee be WFTDA Certified.\\"   \r\n\r\n\\"strongly encouraged\\" doesn\\\'t read like \\"must be\\".  The question is how many refs \\"must be\\" WFTDA certified.  I think the correct answer according to 9.1.1 is \\"none\\".  However, that is not an option.  The options I see are a) 1; b) 2; c) 7; d) 4.', 1),
(296, '90.204.110.172', 1344613739, 596, 0, 'Question #596: I\\\'m reporting question #596 because ... I think the rule reference is wrong? Maybe 6.11.16?', 3),
