(315, '130.88.99.231', 1349444196, 467, 0, 'Question #467: I\\\'m reporting question #467 because ... \r\n\r\nHi sausage it\\\'s Don G.\r\n\r\nI think the question needs to be changed to Downed skater who is out of bounds as that is what the rules say. \r\n\r\n\\"6.8.20 - A downed skater re-entering the track from out of bounds who forces any opposing in-play skaters to fall or lose relative position.\\"\r\n\r\nWhile a downed skater could be one that just fell over, and when they get up everyone loses position as they have re-entered. \r\n\r\nHowever, if this is wrong just ignore me.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGunna go all youtube feedback now!\r\n\r\nThis is bullshit you ruined my streak!!! \r\n\r\n\r\nDon G\r\n\r\n', 2),
