(317, '99.249.69.135', 1349751483, 833, 0, 'Question #833: I\\\'m reporting question #833 because it seems poorly written. There are 2 answers that have initial pass on them but the one says can score points and cannot score points. During a initial pass you can never score points so reading this question I read it assuming this was already known and thought about the next lap around as for scoring points... Donno if its just me but the wording threw me off on this one. ', 3),
