(324, '213.42.182.194', 1351728842, 930, 0, 'Question #930: I\\\'m reporting question #930 because ... The question is worded such that it implies that Jammer B has not yet legitimately passed an in bounds blocker when they lap Jammer A who is in the box. Would the Jammer Lap Point not be applied until Jammer B scores on the first blocker?\r\n\\"8.5 - The Jammer earns a point for each opposing skater who is not on the track immediately upon scoring her first point on an opposing blocker in each scoring pass\\"\r\n', 3),
(325, '67.193.181.146', 1352243177, 568, 0, 'Question #568: I\\\'m reporting question #568 because \r\n\r\nThis is a bit of a trick question. If you remove the word only (which I would do), then the correct answer is B.  Otherwise, the question is ambiguous.', 3),
