(346, '74.84.93.228', 1356899426, 291, 0, 'Question #291: I\\\'m reporting question #291 because ... I think this needs to be re worded a little bit.  By what you say in the question alone, it implies blockers can line up anywhere on the track and in front of the pivot if they are on the line.  Also the rule you site does mention lining up behind a pivot.  Perhaps ad the phrase \\"between the pivot and jammer line and behind the pivot if they are on the line.\\" ', 3);
