(347, '2.25.121.220', 1356900061, 1367, 0, 'Question #1367: I think 6.11.3.2 gives this scenario as an explicit example of cutting - you can still cut track in a no pack situation. I think this is a problem in the wording of rule 6.11.10/11. In fact the opening paragraph of section 6.11 makes reference only to \\\'in bounds\\\' skaters, not \\\'in play\\\'. \r\n\r\n', 3),
(348, '74.198.150.145', 1356904666, 871, 0, 'Question #871: I\\\'m reporting question #871 because ... It refers to calling out minor penalties when the rule noted refers to major penalties ', 2),
(349, '74.84.93.228', 1356908366, 1474, 0, 'Question #1474: I\\\'m reporting question #1474 because ... I believe the rule is 7.3.3, not 7.2.3.', 3),
