(367, '120.151.24.33', 1357016822, 544, 0, 'Question #544: I\\\'m reporting question #544 because ... \r\n\r\nThat should be true. On a No Pack call, if they immediately attempt to reform the pack, they will not get a penalty. 6.10.7 says that. \r\n\r\nUnless there\\\'s a double negative in there that I\\\'m not seeing?  [Changing \\\'but\\\' to \\\'And\\\'?]\r\n\r\n(Also messaged wardrox on reddit)', 3),
