(373, '87.194.199.126', 1357124719, 1378, 0, 'Question #1378: I\\\'m reporting question #1378 because ... being a little petty here but \\\'the\\\' pivot gets to keep their helmet cover on because they are the pivot. The wording is slightly misleading. Perhaps it could say \\\' all four skaters will be allowed to remain on track if the last Pivot to enter the track removes their helmet cover.\\\' or  \\\'all four skaters will be allowed to remain on track if the last Blocker to enter the track wearing the Pivot helmet cover removes their helmet cover.\\\'\r\n\r\nLoving the site, by the way. Thank you.', 3),
(374, '120.151.24.33', 1357125261, 670, 0, 'Question #670: I\\\'m reporting question #670 because ... Suggested rewording (was going through /hard)\r\n\r\n\\"If a skater INTENTIONALLY commits an Illegal Procedure, what sort of Insubordination penalty is this?\\"\r\n\r\n--Rob\r\n', 4),
