(379, '124.168.94.157', 1357134844, 1038, 0, 'Question #1038: I\\\'m reporting question #1038 because ... \r\nALL of these duties can be performed off skates, as NON skating officials. \r\n\r\nrule # 9.1.5 only states  \\"Non-Skating Officials\\"\r\nPerhaps you should change it to rule # 9.1.5.5 to specifically include Jam timer  or re-word the question to ask \\"according to the rules which NSO\\\'s are not officially required\\"? \r\n\r\n', 3),
