(495, '110.32.193.201', 1359637985, 920, 0, 'Question #920: I\\\'m reporting question #920 because ... The question should be \\"When a  jam is called off by a referee due to a skater injury for the second time the skater must sit out\\" A,B,c or D.\r\n\r\nThe question itself eliminates option A, unless you want this to be a trick question.', 3),
