(501, '142.196.22.188', 1359675348, 1279, 0, 'Question #1279: I\\\'m reporting question #1279 because ... \r\n\r\nRule 6.7.8 no longer requires loss of position, and no longer specifies a time limit. It is any impedance of an opponent \\"for any amount of time\\".', 3),
