(503, '99.62.232.189', 1359823499, 1328, 0, 'Question #1328: I\\\'m reporting question #1328 because ...  the wording is very confusing.  Do you mean blocks an opponent in an ADDITIONAL illegal manner on top of the illegal stop block?  The way this is worded a player would be expelled for every stop block, which clearly isnt the case in the rules.', 3),
