(539, '62.254.19.176', 1361259615, 1607, 0, 'Question #1607: I\\\'m reporting question #1607 because ... it asks about cutting in front of an opponent after equipment malfunction, which is a major penalty, then says It\\\'s no impact by rule 6.13.18. Rule 6.13.12 is no impact for cutting one teammate, rule 6.13.18 is a major for an opponent. Rules reference/wording of question/answer wrong.', 3),
