(549, '87.22.233.49', 1361508786, 551, 0, 'Question #551: I\\\'m reporting question #551 because ... The first rule of Roller Derby is Don\\\'t be a Douchebag', 4),
(550, '213.113.2.114', 1361872760, 1156, 0, 'Question #1156: I\\\'m reporting question #1156 because secondary contact with hands or forearms or elbow isn\\\'t always a NI/NP. It can be a major penalty. \r\n\r\nBoth below paragraphs are major penalties:\r\n\r\n\\"6.5.7 - Any illegal contact with hands or forearms above the shoulders.\\"\r\n\r\n\\"6.4.7 - Any illegal contact with the elbow or swinging motion of the elbow that lands above the shoulders.\\"', 1),
